title: Ducklings
transcript:
[A mother duck and her six ducklings.]
[Cueball is in front of the line of ducks, and Megan is behind.]
Megan: Ready?
Cueball: Ready.[The duck and ducklings move.]Cueball: ROAR! BOO![The mother duck is frightened, and turns back. Her six children follow.][Megan snatches the mother duck with a yoink.]
Duck: QUACK![The six ducklings are now trapped in a circle of sorts.]OPERATION: DUCKLING LOOP
